<section class="help-card help-card--compact">
  <div class="help-card__eyebrow">Availability</div>

  <h2 class="help-card__title">
    {{ spaceType.pluralLabel }} in {{ city.city }} may be limited
  </h2>

  <p class="help-card__intro">
    {{ spaceType.label }} space in {{ city.city }} can be available through a mix of listed and off-market opportunities.
    Inventory changes often, and not every option is publicly displayed.
  </p>

  <div class="help-card__grid help-card__grid--tight">
    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Explore the broader market</h3>
      <p>
        Browse the full {{ city.city }} market to get a better sense of location options, building types, and nearby opportunities.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Consider nearby markets</h3>
      <p>
        Nearby cities may offer more availability, different pricing, or space configurations that better match your needs.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Get help finding space</h3>
      <p>
        Tell us what you need and we can help identify {{ spaceType.label | lower }} options that may not be visible online.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 18px; display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
    <a class="btn-primary" href="#market-contact-form">
      Get Help Finding the Right {{ spaceType.label }} Space
    </a>

    <a class="btn-secondary" href="/commercial-real-estate/{{ city.state_abbr }}/{{ city.slug }}/">
      Explore {{ city.city }} Market
    </a>
  </div>
</section>